## 2.python初体验
```python
print(1,2) # print 1 2
print("1" "2") # print 12
print("1","2") # print 1 2
print("hello","world",sep",") #split string using ","

input = input("Enter a word or a number: ") #输入数据都作为字符串接收
input = int(input("Enter a number: ")) # Convert string to int
```
### 3.python基础讲解
python变量特性+命名规则
注释方法
```python
# using # to comment a single line
input = input("Enter your name: ") #get user's name

# using ''' or """ can comment multiple lines
"""
  @version: 3.7
  @author: zoe
  ...
"""
```
python中“：”作用
学会使用dir( )及和help( )
